---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="關於這個網站">
  <section class="about">
    <p class="eyebrow">About the Project</p>
    <h1>關於這個網站</h1>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>關於這個網站</h2>

      <p class="lead">
        這裡不只是肉丸七隨興記錄的內容集合，而是一個隨著時間慢慢展開的內容空間。
      </p>

      <p>
        這裡是肉丸七展開故事與內容的地方。
        透過日記、觀察與創作，記錄那些安靜卻真實的片刻，讓閱讀慢慢成為一種陪伴。
      </p>

      <p>
        肉丸七，誕生於人生走入秋天之後。
        他不只是一個角色，也是一種觀看世界的方式。
        透過這隻熊的視角，日常被重新看見，不急著抵達答案，而是在過程中靜靜前行。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <p class="lead en-lead">
        This is not just a collection of Bearball Seven’s spontaneous writings,
        but a space where ideas and stories unfold gradually over time.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is where Bearball Seven’s stories and ideas continue to grow.
        Through journals, observations, and creative work, it gathers quiet yet
        genuine moments, allowing reading to become a gentle form of
        companionship.
      </p>

      <p>
        Bearball Seven emerged in the autumn stage of life. More than a
        character, he represents a way of seeing the world. Through his
        perspective, everyday life is seen anew—not in search of immediate
        answers, but in the quiet rhythm of moving forward.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-block">
      <h2>關於 Autumnreal Lab</h2>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab 是這一切背後的起點。
        內容、設計與創作思考在此交織，關心的不只是作品本身，
        更在於那些被理解、被感受的瞬間，以及時間如何讓一切慢慢沉澱。
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        在這裡，內容編織成精彩故事。
      </p>

      <p>
        從文章到觀點，從角色創作到品牌實驗，
        這裡逐步累積成一個屬於自己的內容世界，
        讓創作以一種長期而自然的節奏延續下去。
      </p>

      <div class="lang-divider"></div>

      <h3>About Autumnreal Lab</h3>

      <p>
        Autumnreal Lab is the creative origin behind it all. It brings together
        content, design, and creative thinking, with attention not only to what
        is made, but also to how it is understood, felt, and slowly shaped over
        time.
      </p>

      <p class="quote">
        Concepts Shaped, Creative Journeys Told.<br />
        Where ideas become stories.
      </p>

      <p>
        From writing and reflection to character creation and brand exploration,
        this space gradually forms a world of its own, where creative work
        continues as a long-term and natural rhythm.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="ig-wrap">
      <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/bearball.seven/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="ig-link"
      >
        Follow → @bearball.seven
      </a>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8a8a8a;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about-block {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .about h3 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #13335f;
  }

  .lead {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .en-lead {
    color: #2f2f2f;
  }

  .about p {
    max-width: 640px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.95;
    color: #444;
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 28px 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    border-left: 3px solid #d7deea;
    color: #13335f;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .lang-divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    margin: 36px 0 28px;
    background: #e6e6e6;
  }

  .ig-wrap {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .ig-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #13335f;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .ig-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
</style>
